Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.59,Default Box,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(1200,1070)}DYSART ADA DI SETIAP PARTI.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.16,Default Box,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(550,1070)}ADAKAH WILLY RAPAT DENGAN ALAN?
